text: Zillennials (also known as Zennials) are a micro-generation cohort located on the cusp between the Millennials and Generation Z. There is yet to be a definitive definition for Zillennials, with most sources defining this micro- generation as those born from the early 1990s to the early 2000s. The Boston University defines Zillennials as those born from 1992 to 2002. ==References== Category:History Category:Humanities Z Category:Social sciences
title: Zillennials
